{"tid":198480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母又係的士狗","createTime":"2017-04-12T14:08:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T15:27:30.000Z","uid":34348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"57cba0eae092243fb4a42586bd0430086360d355","tid":198480,"uid":34348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:08:02.000Z","msg":"吳女士：「有個跌到起唔到身」<br />\n<br />\n九巴265M下層乘客吳女士向記者表示，意外時九巴被後隨的城巴猛撞，「撞嗰吓好大力」，當時不少乘客站在車廂內，「全部人碌晒去前面地下」，情況非常混亂，「有個跌到起唔到身」。吳女士指，她聽聞現場有人指，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>前面有小巴為避開一輛的士而煞車</strong></span></span>，導致後面多輛車輛煞掣不及。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c390b028839405965c65d9c72ed47cb3c97c2826","tid":198480,"uid":34348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:50:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c70eb39d05df5324900706101c799fb65048a79","tid":198480,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:56:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d81509b9effc006d5341c6a56cf7d62336f685","tid":198480,"uid":40770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T15:25:40.000Z","msg":"積下口德 la"},{"pid":"f169571a854aff94fdf20641c25b167b446b68e9","tid":198480,"uid":6548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T15:27:30.000Z","msg":"樓主積下口德啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}